    "John Trapp": "And the battle increased that day. ] Heb., Ascended. Josephus then is out sure, who saith that Ahab only was slain that day, and all the army escaped.\nVer.\n35. And the battle increased that day.] Heb., Ascended. Josephus then is out sure, who saith that Ahab only was slain that day, and all the army escaped.\nVer."
